creator: ABB Information Systems AG
descriptionHtml:
Nexus® Pro is designed to enable building owners and managers to easily maintain and test emergency lighting, without the need to visually verify performance or disrupt the power supply. All operations can be managed remotely, giving building owners and managers complete control wherever they are, whenever they need it the most.

You can increase productivity, reduce testing costs, and gain access to real-time data right form your smartphone. With its clean, simple interface, the Nexus®Pro app is as fast and easy to set up as it is to navigate.
descriptionShort: Nexus® Pro is an IOT cost saving solution designed to assure emergency lighting.
title: Nexus®Pro

creator: ABB Information Systems AG
descriptionHtml:
Naveo®Pro system allows customers to set up, maintain and fully control their entire emergency lighting installation with a new mobile app.

This provides a real time overview of all systems, saving time, enabling better maintenance planning and enhancing building safety.
descriptionShort: Smart monitoring system to manage emergency lighting with a mobile app.

- Fix for false lost of connection with remote data for certain views.
